     'Something went wrong with the ZIP file'Assert fileList{(в€§/вЌєв€ЉвЌµ)в€§(в€§/вЌµв€ЉвЌє)}zipContent
     3 вЋ•NDELETE targetFolder,'/Tatin.dyalog'  вЌќ Because until 0.61.0 the user command script was a sibling of the Tatin/ folder
     :If batchFlag
         вЋ•OFF
     :Else
         вЋ•в†ђ'*** Done;  note that the Tatin project has been closed'
     :EndIf
 :EndIf
